<h1 id="java-escpos-print-utility">Java ESC/POS Print Utility</h1>
<hr>
<p>This utility runs a server on port 7655 and accepts post request with json as follow:</p>
<pre class=" language-json"><code class="prism  language-json"><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">"type"</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">"INVOICE"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">"nameOfPrinter"</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">"Epson"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">"content"</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token string">"&lt;CTL_LF&gt;HEADER&lt;TXT_ALIGN_CT&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;CTL_LF&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">"printerSize"</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token number">58</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>  
</code></pre>
<p>This will print the value of <b>content</b> passed json using the printer with name <b>Epson</b>.<br>
Printer Size is used to set the value of <b>divider<b> and <b>Horizontal Tab</b>.</b></b></p>
<hr>
